					<h3 class="mtext-111 cl2 p-b-16">
						Our Story
					</h3>

					<p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
						Founded in 1962, our family-owned gold jewelry shop has been a beacon of trust, craftsmanship, and timeless beauty for over six decades. What started as a small endeavor in the heart of the city has grown into a cherished destination for exquisite, hand-crafted gold jewelry, celebrating tradition and modern artistry. Every piece we create tells a story—of love, heritage, and celebration—and we pride ourselves on being part of your most special moments.
					</p>

					<p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
						From generation to generation, our passion for creating beautiful jewelry has only grown. We specialize in both readymade and predesigned collections, ensuring that each customer finds something that resonates with their personal style and cultural values. Our designs blend classic elegance with contemporary trends, making them perfect for any occasion, be it a wedding, an anniversary, or just an expression of self-love.
					</p>

					<p class="stext-113 cl6 p-b-26">
						Have any questions? Visit us at 38/A D S Dudley Senanayake Mawatha, Colombo 00800 or call us on 0112 678 181. Our dedicated team is always here to assist you.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

